<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/23746243">把自己伪装得高大上去达成生活、事业、情感上的目标真的好吗？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1680152" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"></div>


</div>
